**Overall meaning:**

Then Sankriti asked the Sun god, "O Lord, please tell me the knowledge of Brahman." The Sun god said, "Listen, Sankriti, I will tell you the knowledge of the Truth, which is very difficult to obtain. By simply knowing it, you will become liberated while alive." 
